  "prompt": "A magical stave (galdrastafur) inspired by Icelandic runic tradition. The design features a central 'Helm of Awe' (Ægishjálmur) structure with eight arms, overlaid with bindrunes made from Þ (Thurisaz), Eolh (ᛉ), and Tiwaz (ᛏ), forming protective thorns and spikes. Inverted Isa (ᛁ) runes are placed at the cardinal points to freeze hostile energy. A 'Runic Eye' motif is in the center, surrounded by concentric rings. The overall style is traditional Icelandic magic, symmetrical, black ink on parchment, intricate and powerful, with a focus on protection, reversal, and spiritual sovereignty. The stave is named 'Skuggsjálmr' (The Shadow-Helm).",
