  "prompt": "A custom magical stave inspired by the traditional Icelandic Veiðistafur, adapted into a modern poetic bindrune-sigil style. The stave is composed within three concentric circles intersected by an 11-pointed hendecagram star, with runes and symbolic arrows radiating outward. The central design contains mirrored bindrunes representing protection, hunting, and spiritual sovereignty. Fine, fractal-like lines and geometric forms weave through the structure, fusing Norse magic with a cyber-shamanic aesthetic. Rendered in black ink on aged parchment, with a mystical, hand-drawn feel.",
